Package space.sunqian.annotations

Annotation Interface DefaultNonNull

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Nonnull(when=ALWAYS) @TypeQualifierNickname @Target({TYPE,METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR,PACKAGE}) @TypeQualifierDefault({METHOD,FIELD,PARAMETER,LOCAL_VARIABLE,TYPE_PARAMETER,TYPE_USE}) public @interface DefaultNonNull
Declares all methods, fields, parameters, local variables, type parameters, and type uses under the scope of the annotated element must be non-null.

It is equivalent to use Nonnull on all those points.
